  <brief_title>Treatment of Language and Memory in Patients With Alzheimer's Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>Treatment of Language and Memory in Patients With Alzheimer's Disease: A Comparison Between Drug Therapy and Drug Therapy Plus Behavioral Intervention</official_title>
